<br>
from levels around 1-30, AF is very nice, and having Very high af is good.  After 30 player made stuff goes to hell and you get this junk (that gives nice +hp and stuff) out of dungeons which works as armor until 50.  soo since you arent going to get anything over 89 quality (except rare quest stuff), you might as well go all out stats at these levels.  Adding +200 hp and like +40 con makes a big difference for the maybe 20-30 af you trade for it.<br>
<br>
More importantly, know what kinda weapons the mob you fight uses.  If you see a blue con with a 2handed slash weapon, look for another mob to kill, cause that blue is going hit you as hard as an orange.  I find mobs using 2 handed thrust, or crushing are the best for me to try to solo (you never see a 1h thrust mob in albion except for the 30 epic).  Take advantage of slow weapons like pikes, where if you evade or they miss you get many many chances to  do damage (and you get armor bonuses if they do hit), and avoid stuff like halberds which hit you for insane amounts of damage.  Also avoid mobs using fast slashing weapons if possible, they hurt a lot too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2001.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2001.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2001.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2001.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=2001.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2001.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2001.topic>